long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Golden Moon is a chrome extension that injects CSS code into replit.com to make it look nicer. It is meant to only work in dark mode (hence its name). It makes replit.com's code easier to read, and it gives the viewer higher visibility for reading.
